assertion: Instead of rock, paper, scissors, I prefer to play my own version of the game which is worm, pigeon, shotgun.
I am in an ongoing feud with a cat who walked a hundred miles to torment me.
After a mix-up in a tattoo parlour, we now have each other's tattoo.
He is my ex-boyfriend and I used to put sleeping pill in my parents' tea to slip him into the house.
Whilst staying at an Airbnb, I mistook him for an intruder and attacked him with a whisk.
I was genuinely invited to Harry and Meghan's wedding today, but I said no because I had to come here and do this.
